title: Haunted Canada - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/30/22

description:
George Noory and author Mark Leslie explore some of his favorite stories of supernatural events from across Canada, like mind control experiments, a levitating woman at a mental hospital, UFO sightings, and the ghost of a woman who may or may not have been murdered.
